                     <note type="general">8 lines</note>
                     <note type="general">Written along the fibers on the recto</note>
                     <note type="general">Upper margin of 0.5 cm</note>
                     <note type="general">P.Duk.inv. 466 was formerly P.Miss. 32</note>
